quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  26,34,"Inna i imvebbôen i s d izzin: \"wagi, s tidep, d aseêêar amusnaw"
  26,35,"ib$a a kwen issuffe$, s ssêur is, seg wakal nnwen. D acu t lameô nnwen"
  26,36,"Nnan: \"sgani t, neppa akked gma s; azen ineccaden ar temdinin"
  26,37,ad ak d awin yal aseêêar amusnaw
  26,38,"Mlalen iseêêaren, di lweqt akked wass ipwassnen"
  26,39,"Nnan i imdanen: \"ma ad tenjemâam"
  26,40,"Ahat a neddu d iseêêaren, ma d nitni ara irebêen"
  26,41,"Mi d usan iseêêaren, nnan as i Ferâun: \"ma ad a$ tili teqdiât, ma nerbeê"
  26,42,"Inna: \"ih, d$a, kunwi, war ccekk, a ppu$alem seg iqôiben"
  26,43,"Inna yasen Musa: \"veggôet ayen ara tveggôem"
  26,44,"Veggôen imraren akked tâakwzin nnsen. Nnan: \"s tezmert n Ferâun, ard nekwni ara irebêen"
  26,45,Iveggeô Musa taâkwazt is. Apan tesseblaâ ayen id snulfan
  26,46,"Iseêêaren $lin, knan"
  26,47,"Nnan: \"numen s Mass imavalen"
  26,48,Mass n Musa akked Haôun
  26,49,"Inna: \"tumnem yiS, uqbel ma serrêe$ awen? Neppa, war ccekk, d ameqwôan nnwen i wen issêefven ssêur. A ppeéôem, ad awen gezme$ afus sya, avaô sya; a kwen ûûemôe$ akw $ef umidag"
  26,50,"Nnan: \"ulac u$ilif, acku ar Mass nne$, ara nezzi"
  26,51,"Ih, nessaram ad Isemmeê, Mass nne$, tuccva nne$ imi aql a$ d lmumnin imenza"
  26,52,"Nweêêa i Musa: \"ôôuê s ugdud iW, deg iv, acku a kwen in vefôen"